      <hr><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1>400 - Series Statement/Added Entry-Personal Name (R)</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - Local</div>
      <div class="datename">February 1999</div>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%">
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td width="45%"><strong>First Indicator</strong><br><em>Type of personal name entry element</em><br>0 - Forename <br>1 - Surname <br>3 - Family name <br><br></td>
            <td width="45%"><strong>Second Indicator</strong><br><em>Pronoun represents main entry</em><br>0 - Main entry not represented by pronoun <br>1 - Main entry represented by pronoun <br><br></td>
         </tr>
      </table>
