      <hr>
      <h3>CONVERSION TO CURRENT FIELDS</h3>
	  <p><em>If indicator 2 is 0:</em></p>
      <p>4XX indicator 1 and all subfields except subfield $x convert to 8XX with same
                        indicator 1 value and same subfields,
      </p>
      <p><u>and</u> 4XX $t, $v, $x are also copied to 490 $a,$v,$x, respectively; 490
                        indicator 1 is set to 1.
      </p>
	  <p><em>If indicator 2 is 1:</em></p>
      <p>4XX indicator 1 and all subfields except subfields $a and $x convert to 8XX with same
                        indicator 1 value and same subfields,
      </p>
      <p><u>and</u> all 1XX subfields are copied into the same 8XX, preceeding the subfields
                        from the 4XX field
      </p>
      <p><u>and</u> 4XX $t, $v, $x are also copied to 490 $a,$v,$x, respectively; 490
                        indicator 1 is set to 1.
      </p>
     
